{"tid":283290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府從無承諾推行標準工時","createTime":"2017-06-14T05:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T10:45:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26365119c24f292dfa696d08bd861a5a95c6ac64","tid":283290,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170614/s00001/6e36be0bb320d5a1e801811ff3da5b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170614%2Fs00001%2F6e36be0bb320d5a1e801811ff3da5b51.jpg&h=efc9190b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究標準工時多時，政府昨提出「合約工時」方案，被勞工界狠批「偷換概念」。政務司長張建宗今早晤傳媒時表示，政府建議的「合約工時」方案是「穩妥起步點」，並非「終點」，又強調政府從無承諾推行標準工時。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，政府決策已考慮過去3年多大量數據分析和研究，而1.1萬元是基於2016年數據，到最快2020年底立法時，當局會再參考屆時工資數據，形容「實際上推出的水平可能不是1.1萬元，有空間調校」。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又強調，「政府取態從頭到尾是開放態度，無一個承諾推行標準工時」。他續說，標準工時相當複雜，不能一刀切，重申今次是穩妥、務實起步點，「如果連起步點都不行，對各方無好處」。"},{"pid":"ab275c61511ee7fbbebf13819937341f75b3d1a1","tid":283290,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170614/s00001/1497410079528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170614%2Fs00001%2F1497410079528&d=fGBCbTgfTb2PkxpjPpctbS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4d2e598b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170614%2Fs00001%2F1497410079528&h=c41eefe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170614/s00001/1497410079528</a>"},{"pid":"f6d44c8f4484cdd9c28d0429ae98ff8b28ecbae0","tid":283290,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"549d166edf1734a6407907e2f354d62dfc2ae5a0","tid":283290,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201